<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-07-08T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-07-08T19:00:00-05:00" n="149" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d149">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">724.34119/1456: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Weddell</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Buenos
                                        Aires</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-07-08T20:00:00-04:00">July 8, 1938—8
                                p.m.</date><lb/>[Received 9:12 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>188. From Braden. My 187, July 8, 11 a.m. To the last paragraph of
                            article I before [<hi rend="italic">after?</hi>] “paragraph” insert the
                            following: “The said line will not go on the Pilcomayo River more to the
                            east than to Pozo Hondo, nor to the west further than any point on the
                            line which, starting from D’Orbigny, was fixed by the Neutral Military
                            Commission as intermediary between the maximum positions reached by the
                            belligerent armies at the suspension of fire on June 14, 1935.”</p>
                        <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                        <closer><signed> [Braden] <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Weddell</hi>
                            </signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>